author: Milford Mirror
title: Girls swimming: Ava Corsi double winner for Lions
text:
By Milford Mirror on October 4, 2015 in High School Sports , Sports features · 0 Comments 
Foran High dropped a 99-85 decision to Sheehan High from Wallingford in SCC girls swimming and diving on Friday. 
Earning victories for coach Kristin Skuches’ Lions (2-3) were 200 IM: Sarah Fitzgerald, 2:24.83; 50 freestyle: Ava Corsi, 27.14; diving: Emma Longley, 251.65; and 100 freestyle: Corsi, 59.19. Related posts:
